{"tid":370563,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【千杯不醉】81蚊食自助餐 男客豪飲逾200支啤酒","createTime":"2017-08-23T06:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T10:03:16.000Z","uid":30049,"like":248,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc75626def743dcdb295362c41556dab73192e93","tid":370563,"uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"即時兩岸  2017-08-22 16:51:12 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170822/large/1503389937_2596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170822%2Flarge%2F1503389937_2596.jpg&h=cad586c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170822/large/1503389936_4261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170822%2Flarge%2F1503389936_4261.jpg&h=c85648b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170822/large/1503389938_f5ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170822%2Flarge%2F1503389938_f5ae.jpg&h=37e1ea1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170822/large/1503389939_af13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170822%2Flarge%2F1503389939_af13.jpg&h=7074a066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n香港人鍾愛吃自助餐，個別食肆甚至提供「酒水任飲」服務。客人都竭盡所能，免得蝕底。惟昨日，重慶一名90後男客到楊家坪一家自助餐店吃自助餐。他付了68元(人民幣‧下同；約81港元)的自助餐費用後，竟喝掉200多支啤酒。<br />\n<br />\n看到男客狂灌200多支啤酒，老闆欲哭無淚調侃說：「你腸胃是『下水道』(類似酒筲箕的意思)嗎？這麼能喝，我店收費本來就低，像你這樣一喝，我要虧本了。」<br />\n<br />\n據自助餐店的職員表示，男客坐下不久，便開始從雪櫃取出拿30瓶冰啤酒，不消一會便喝光，繼而再取60支啤酒。男客後來乾脆直接要求職員拿出15箱，這樣他先後喝光200多支啤酒。有其他食客見狀，直言他是中國「啤酒王」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170822&amp;guid=57113020&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170822%26guid%3D57113020%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=upHURH%2BY6M7wXchtIaTU5ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=72e86690\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170822%26guid%3D57113020%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=783b18b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170822&amp;guid=57113020&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線水都飲唔到啦仲要啤酒咁多氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6e10ddf3d976b19371f114f01c3f9c2e25e548","tid":370563,"uid":34489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"咁咪係咁痾尿"},{"pid":"87b7e65005ddb6a8b9bdf27e015ffddcf09ce989","tid":370563,"uid":73785,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"大陸人特色"},{"pid":"1151ef22a37a4701912bb1ece7cbe107f8fb3eda","tid":370563,"uid":69760,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"咁都唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f665a57fcb39c8d132bb58a7748b04481ae2c12c","tid":370563,"uid":40397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"應該好快唔係度"},{"pid":"3d220efbc4ea2e2a38270e63b600afdb1a8b6299","tid":370563,"uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"任食自助餐 比盡你都係3個鐘<br />\n姐係每個鐘飲66支<br />\n一分鐘一支有多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e7e09d46c4d64905101a6bc8bc555795c1bf5a","tid":370563,"uid":53105,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"假酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif