ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n200/400=6成？<br />\n有數神快拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n15箱+90枝<br />\n一箱當你10支都過200呀<br />\n200多支識唔識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a070f25d94c3aa3e42518010cc4f0d49058a1452","tid":370563,"uid":3268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似炒作間野多 飲咁多唔酒精中毒都水中毒死Q左</blockquote><br />\n 假酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdf1b679cf660b44cbd79591c34faaabb30e8ec","tid":370563,"uid":10520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"假新聞多"},{"pid":"c573b533fdc55c146b0df023d87d2bb07e09432f","tid":370563,"uid":28515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"炒作"},{"pid":"c2e8ac4aa4ad0127f77edc7891ba90d0865c5a07","tid":370563,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"200枝有無可能<br />\n成個個重左150公斤"},{"pid":"81b670808834a57d5deabf1b887b5ce81c902470","tid":370563,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:04:33.000Z","msg":"假酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1402ef996e6cbe45bfd8e995bfcc6395e57e14a","tid":370563,"uid":33359,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"段譽登感酒氣刺鼻，有些不大好受。但依舊毫不遲疑的喝了下去。那大漢見他喝得這般豪爽，端起碗來，也是仰脖喝乾。<br />\n<br />\n段譽未喝第三碗酒時，已感煩惡欲嘔，待得又是半斤烈酒灌入腹中，五臟六腑似乎都欲翻轉。他緊緊閉口，不讓腹中酒水嘔將出來。突然間丹田中一動，一股真氣沖將上來，體內酒氣竟與真氣相混，小指之中，卻有一道酒水緩緩流出。段譽暗叫：「妙極！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b3fb468916fd806cc4ab470bcf99876a105081","tid":370563,"uid":45773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"中水毒加中酒毒"},{"pid":"a54fbd4a